  "texts": [
    "In other words, the area covered by patent applications expands its space.",
    "In contrast, the size of the scientific frontier covered by research papers is relatively stable.",
    "Next, its dynamics in the science-technology space is analyzed.",
    "The science intensity of patents increases on average (from 4.71 neighbor papers in the 1990s to 7.40 neighbor papers in the 2010s), while the share of patents with no research paper as a neighbor document does not change significantly (58.1% in the 1990s and 59.0% in the 2010s).",
    "In contrast, the technology intensity of papers decreases on average (from 25.7 neighbor patents in the 1990s to 20.2 neighbor patents in the 2010s), and the share of papers with no patent as a neighbor increases (from 20.0% in the 1990s to 37.0% in the 2010s)."
